Current revenue and net revenue from financial transactions fell to zero compared to the previous year, revenue from liabilities and certain securities as well as the dissolution of liabilities in the credit business fell by more than 70 percent to EUR 5 million.
Only thanks to higher revenues from reimbursements of subsequent settlement costs from the restructuring of the former Depfa Group, as well as from the reimbursement of interest according to the tax regulations and from the provision of business for group companies, the revenue minus was still moderate, at around 16 percent.
